leaflet-velocity
================

Vendored version: 1.7.0
Upstream: https://github.com/onaci/leaflet-velocity (tag v1.7.0)
License: MIT  (package.json "license": "MIT")

The minified bundle vendored here (leaflet-velocity.min.js) had its license
header stripped during minification. This file restores the upstream license
notices. leaflet-velocity 1.7.0 is distributed under the MIT License and
incorporates code under MIT from Cameron Beccario (the "earth"/Windy renderer)
and Stanislav Sumbera (L.CanvasLayer.js). The three MIT notices below are
reproduced verbatim from the upstream LICENSE file for tag v1.7.0.

Note: leaflet-velocity 2.x and later relicensed to the CSIRO Open Source
Software Licence Agreement. The version vendored here (1.7.0) predates that
change and remains MIT.

